import React from 'react'
import styled from 'styled-components'


const Container = styled.div``
const Left = styled.div``
const Center = styled.div``
const Right = styled.div``


const Footer = () => {
  return (
    <Container>
        <Left></Left>
        <Center></Center>
        <Right></Right>
    </Container>
  )
}

export default Footer
